1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:02,440
Tell me, who is this Ateş Karahan?

2
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:04,360
So you will not talk, huh?

3
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:05,400
Fine.

4
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:08,840
Then I will go to Ateş and tell him every scheme you pulled behind his back.

5
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:10,320
Go ahead, tell him.

6
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:13,000
I do not even care if I die.

7
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,560
If you truly want Mercan…

8
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:17,160
…do not ever stand against me.

9
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:19,720
You cannot do anything without me.

10
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:23,640
Did you come here to remember why we came here in the first place?

11
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:29,920
It has no meaning anymore.

12
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:34,960
Since you have set off on a path with the girl…

13
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:37,920
You swore revenge for years.

14
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:41,360
Your mother’s, father’s, Eylül’s bones are aching in their graves.

15
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,880
Mother Müzeyyen!

16
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:46,120
My mother suddenly walked out of my life, left me.

17
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:48,120
I did not even know she was pregnant.

18
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:49,800
Why did you never call her?

19
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:53,040
She said she was in love with someone else and left.

20
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:55,400
She never let anyone else into her life.

21
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:57,680
If I had known she was pregnant…

22
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,000
Your wife, Nermin…

23
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:01,760
…when she learned my mother was pregnant…

24
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:05,040
…threatened her with me.

25
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:07,360
You threatened her and scared her.

26
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:08,520
Enough already!

27
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:11,520
Do you have no shame asking your wife about the mistress who ran away?

28
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:12,680
Do not drive me crazy, woman.

29
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:14,920
You had one son.

30
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,080
And he is under the ground.

31
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:20,920
No matter what you say, you cannot cover up the evil you did.

32
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:26,800
It is time to learn the truth about Ateş, Ms. Mercan.

33
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:32,000
Let us see if you will still be able to have breakfast so cheerfully then.

34
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,640
Do not let your coffee get cold.

35
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,000
All right.

36
